\",\"integration-disabled-v2\":\"This integration has been disabled by your {product} administrator.\",\"intelligent-mind-map-layout-control-horizontal-layout\":\"Horizontal layout\",\"intelligent-mind-map-layout-control-set-layout\":\"Set layout\",\"intelligent-mind-map-layout-control-vertical-layout\":\"Vertical layout\",\"it-IT--jira-card-dependencies-label-v2.one\":\"{count} elemento di lavoro collegato\",\"it-IT--jira-card-dependencies-label-v2.other\":\"{count} elementi di lavoro collegati\",\"ja--jira-card-dependencies-label-v2.one\":\"{count} linked work item\",\"ja--jira-card-dependencies-label-v2.other\":\"{count}件のリンクされた作業項目\",\"jira-authentication-add-instance-contact-admin\":\"To connect to a new Jira instance, please contact your account admin.\",\"jira-authentication-no-access-to-instance-contact-admin\":\"You don't have access to this Jira instance. Please contact support.\",\"jira-authentication-no-admin-credentials-v3\":\"Our Lucid Cards for Jira integration now supports live updates from Jira. To enable this functionality, please ask your account admin to configure your Jira instance in the Lucid admin panel.\",\"jira-bulk-conversion-ui-both-fields-exceed-limits\":\"One or more selected shapes exceed Jira's character limits. Summary limit: {summaryLimit} characters, Description limit: {descriptionLimit} characters. Shorten the text before converting.\",\"jira-bulk-conversion-ui-convert-button\":\"Convert\",\"jira-bulk-conversion-ui-converting-button\":\"Converting...\",\"jira-bulk-conversion-ui-description-exceeds-limit\":\"One or more selected shapes have descriptions exceeding Jira's limit of {limit} characters. Shorten the description text before converting.\",\"jira-bulk-conversion-ui-description-text\":\"Text on each selected shape will be used as the description field in Jira.\",\"jira-bulk-conversion-ui-empty-shapes-v2\":\"The shapes selected have an empty text field. To create Jira work items, text on shape is used as the 'summary' in Jira which is a required field.\",\"jira-bulk-conversion-ui-next-button\":\"Next\",\"jira-bulk-conversion-ui-summary\":\"Summary\",\"jira-bulk-conversion-ui-summary-description\":\"Text on each selected shape will be used as the summary field in Jira.\",\"jira-bulk-conversion-ui-summary-exceeds-limit\":\"One or more selected shapes have summaries exceeding Jira's limit of {limit} characters. Shorten the summary text before converting.\",\"jira-bulk-conversion-ui-title-v2.one\":\"Convert {count} shape to Jira work item\",\"jira-bulk-conversion-ui-title-v2.other\":\"Convert {count} shapes to Jira work items\",\"jira-bulk-conversion-ui-too-many-shapes\":\"We cannot convert more than {count} shapes at a time. Please select fewer shapes and try again.\",\"jira-callout-mapping-fields-onboarding\":\"Optimize your Jira integration by mapping data fields to Lucid.\",\"jira-callout-visualize-linked-work-items\":\"Visualize linked work items\",\"jira-card-status-bulk-edit-disable-reason-v2\":\"Bulk editing Jira status requires the selected work items to be from the same project and have identical statuses.\",\"jira-cards-highlight-fields-description\":\"Manage your Lucid Cards for Jira settings here.\",\"jira-cards-linked-to-different-instance-no-edit\":\"This card and this board are linked to different Jira instances. You will be unable to edit this card on this board.\",\"jira-cards-spotlight-description-v4\":\"Lucid cards for Jira accelerates your agile planning. Easily create, import, and update Jira work items directly in Lucidspark.\",\"jira-cards-spotlight-header-v2\":\"Elevate your planning and roadmapping with Lucid Cards for Jira\",\"jira-cards-spotlight-primary-button-v3\":\"Import Jira work items\",\"jira-configure-fields-prompt-cancel\":\"Cancel\",\"jira-configure-fields-prompt-description\":\"Optimize your Jira integration by mapping data fields to Lucid.\",\"jira-configure-fields-prompt-primary-button-v2\":\"Map data\",\"jira-configure-fields-prompt-title\":\"Map your Jira fields to Lucid\",\"jira-conversion-converting-work-item-growl.one\":\"Converting Jira work item...\",\"jira-conversion-converting-work-item-growl.other\":\"Converting Jira work items...\",\"jira-conversion-creation-successful-growl-v2.one\":\"{count} Jira work item created successfully.\",\"jira-conversion-creation-successful-growl-v2.other\":\"{count} Jira work items created successfully.\",\"jira-conversion-jira-api-error-v2.one\":\"Unable to create Jira work item. Your Jira instance returned the following error: \",\"jira-conversion-jira-api-error-v2.other\":\"Unable to create Jira work items. Your Jira instance returned the following error: \",\"jira-conversion-sign\":\"Sign in\",\"jira-conversion-signin-incorrect-credentials-v2.one\":\"You are authenticated with a different Jira instance. To convert this shape to a Jira work item, <w0>Sign in</w0> and re-authenticate with the correct instance.\",\"jira-conversion-signin-incorrect-credentials-v2.other\":\"You are authenticated with a different Jira instance. To convert these shapes to Jira work items, <w0>Sign in</w0> and re-authenticate with the correct instance.\",\"jira-conversion-signin-no-credentials-v2.one\":\"You are not authenticated with Jira. <w0>Sign in</w0> to convert this shape to a Jira work item.\",\"jira-conversion-signin-no-credentials-v2.other\":\"You are not authenticated with Jira. <w0>Sign in</w0> to convert these shapes to Jira work items.\",\"jira-conversion-ui-convert-button\":\"Convert\",\"jira-conversion-ui-converting-button\":\"Converting...\",\"jira-conversion-ui-description-v3\":\"Fill all required fields to convert and create a new Jira work item.\",\"jira-conversion-ui-next-button\":\"Next\",\"jira-conversion-ui-title-v2\":\"Convert to Jira work item\",\"jira-convert-into-jira-work-items-message-description\":\"Turn selected Lucid cards into Jira work items. Updates made in Jira will be reflected in Lucid and vice versa, keeping everything aligned.\",\"jira-convert-into-ji